Introduction

This is the first post to this attempt at a blog. I guess since this is the first post this is where I tell you what type of content to expect in this blog. Which is something that I am wondering myself as I do not know what I would like to write about. I guess you can expect to see random bits of what I am learning or trying to learn on a daily basis. So in summary I guess this is the following content you might see here.

  • Attemps at C#.net Core.
  • A lot of JavaScript.
  • A lot of PHP.
  • Games?
